<ul class="project-title-and-text">
    <li class="project-title">
        Letters To A Young Poet
    </li>

    <li class="project-type">
        Book Design
    </li>

    <li class="project-tools">
        InDesign, Photoshop
    </li>

    <li class="project-objective-title">
        About
    </li>

    <li class="project-body-text">
        A booklet designed around an excerpt from Rainer Maria Rilke's Letters to a Young Poet, a text fundamentally
        about patience, uncertainty, and the slow work of becoming. The image selection reflects that theme directly:
        paint drying, a bell pepper ripening, a quilt being knitted — things that cannot be rushed.
    </li>
</ul>

